# Architecture & data model

Full detail: `.playbook/03_ARCHITECTURE.md`, `.playbook/09_DATA_MODEL.md`.

- Shape: `data/*.json` → `Render` (`assets/js/render.js`) → thin `index.html` (fetch + shell + wiring).
- UI never owns data. Serve over HTTP locally (`file://` blocks `fetch` — DR-005).
- Stable `id` per record; unknown fields `null`/`"Unknown"`; dates ISO 8601.
- No request-time build. Exception: `npm run prerender` bakes data into committed HTML/sitemap (DR-022); `verify` fails on drift.
